                            <comment id="75882" author="adilger" created="Wed, 29 Jan 2014 18:35:15 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;This &quot;unexpected timeout&quot; problem was also hit on LU-4549 (now TEI-1443), but even before the test was running for 3600s.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="75787" author="adilger" created="Tue, 28 Jan 2014 18:42:29 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;This might be caused by TEI-1403.  The test_45 code was running fine, and then within a few seconds of the test starting it was declared a timeout and stacks dumped and rebooted.  There is no indication in the logs that the test failed or the node crashed.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
